title: Natura Si - Gustavo Fara
description: Part of chain of organic food and products store throughout Milan and northern Italy. Has a deli. Organic, vegan, vegetarian, macrobiotic, gluten-free, sugar-free products, natural cleaning products and toiletries, pet food, and organic, supplements, beauty products, and books. From main exit of Centrale station there is a big square in front, take the street in the far right corner. From there Via Gustavo Fara is the 2nd left.
